\c 24
\s Rugwaro rwekurambana
\p
\v 1 Kana murume achitora mukadzi, ndokumuwana, ndokuitika kana asingawani nyasha pameso ake, nokuti awana chinyadzo kwaari, zvino ngaamunyorere rugwaro rwekurambana agopa muruoko rwake ndokumubudisa mumba make.
\v 2 Kana abuda mumba make, angaendawo ndokuva weumwe murume;
\v 3 kana murume anotevera akamuvenga ndokumunyorera rugwaro rwekumuramba ndokupa muruoko rwake ndokumubudisa mumba make; uye kana murume anotevera \add uyu\add* achifa wanga amutora kuva mukadzi wake;
\v 4 murume wake wekutanga, wakamubudisa, haangamutorizve kuva mukadzi wake shure kwekusvibiswa; nokuti chinyangadzo pamberi paJehovha. Naizvozvo haungatadzisi nyika iyo Jehovha Mwari wako yaanokupa kuva nhaka.
\p
\v 5 Kana munhu acha\add ngo\add*tora mukadzi mutsva, haangabuduri hondo, uye haangabatiswi chero basa ripi; achava akasununguka kumba kwake gore rimwe, kuti afadze mukadzi wake waatora.
\s Zvekupika nezvekuba nezvemaperembudzi
\p
\v 6 Hakuna munhu achatora guyo kana huyo kubatisa; nokuti anotora upenyu kubatisa.
\p
\v 7 Kana munhu akawanikwa achiba munhu pahama dzake kuvana vaIsraeri, ndokumubata senhapwa kana kumutengesa, mbavha iyo ichafa; saizvozvo uchabvisa kuipa kubva pakati pako.
\p
\v 8 Chenjera pahosha yemaperembudzi, kuchenjerera nekuita zvichienderana nezvese vapristi VaRevhi zvavanokudzidzisa; sezvandakavaraira, chenjererai kuzviita.
\v 9 Rangarira Jehovha Mwari wako zvaakaitira Miriamu panzira pakubuda kwenyu muEgipita.
\p
\v 10 Kana uchikweretesa umwe wako chinhu, usapinda mumba make kuti utore rubatso rwake.
\v 11 Uchamira panze, uye munhu waunokweretesa achakubudisira rubatso panze.
\v 12 Zvino kana ari munhu murombo, usarara nerubatso rwake.
\v 13 Zvirokwazvo uchadzosera rubatso kwaari pakuvira kwezuva, kuti arare nenguvo yake, uye akuropafadze; uye zvichava kururama kwauri pamberi paJehovha Mwari wako.
\p
\v 14 Usadzvinyirira muranda wakahaiwa murombo uye anoshaiwa, pahama dzako kana pamutorwa wako ari munyika yako mukati memasuwo ako.
\v 15 Uchapa mubairo wake nezuva rake, uye \add mubairo\add* urege kuvirirwa nezuva, nokuti murombo, uye wakaisa moyo wake pauri; zvimwe angakuchemera kuna Jehovha, chikava chivi kwauri.
\p
\v 16 Madzibaba haangaurawi nekuda kwevana, uye nevana havangaurawi nekuda kwemadzibaba; munhu umwe neumwe achaurawa nekuda kwechivi chake.
\s Tsitsi kuchirikadzi nenherera nevatorwa
\p
\v 17 Usatsausa mutongo wemutorwa \add ne\add*nherera; uye usatora nguvo yechirikadzi kuva rubatso.
\v 18 Asi ucharangarira kuti waiva muranda muEgipita, Jehovha Mwari wako ndokukudzikunuramo; naizvozvo ndinokuraira kuita chinhu ichi.
\p
\v 19 Paunokohwa goho rako mumunda wako, ndokukanganwa chisumbu mumunda, haungadzokeri kunochitora, chichava chemutorwa, chenherera, nechechirikadzi, kuti Jehovha Mwari wako akuropafadze pabasa rese remaoko ako.
\v 20 Kana uchizunza muti wako wemuorivhi, usatsvakisisa matavi shure kwako; zvichava zvemutorwa nezvenherera nezvechirikadzi.
\v 21 Kana uchiunganidza mazambiringa emunda wako wemizambiringa, usatsvakisisa shure kwako; achava emutorwa neenherera neechirikadzi.
\v 22 Ucharangarira kuti waiva muranda munyika yeEgipita; naizvozvo ndinokuraira chinhu ichi.